name: Square Vintage Resin Ring, Size 9

name: .Chica*Plástica. [1!]
description:
We are so proud to introduce our new Eco-friendly collection [Chica*Plástica]. 

Plastic bags are perhaps the most used item which we do not have the facility to recycle, besides re-use. Through a process where heat is applied, the plastic bags fuse together resulting in a super sturdy textile, 100% recycled plastic.

These super lightweight earrings feature hand painted oval pieces, a green star bead, a neon yellow seed bead, a vintage faceted plastic round bead and a peace sign charm.


All our jewelry is handcrafted with Silver Plated findings.
